    "Each turn is given an emotional label based on majority agreement.",
    "In line with previous research, only four emotion categoriesTable 3 A comparison between four generative models VAE Flow GAN Diffusion Goal VAEs (variational autoencoders) maximize the evidence lower bound (ELBO), which implicitly maximizes the log-likelihood of the data A flow-based generative model is built via a series of invertible transformations.",
